# === Agent Genesis Configuration ===

# LLM Billing Verification (ZKTLS via Reclaim Protocol)
# These keys enable billing-based mining score boost.
# Your API key stays LOCAL on this machine — it is NEVER sent to any server.
# The ZKTLS proof only extracts verified billing data (label + usage amount),
# your key itself is cryptographically hidden.
#
# Currently supported: openrouter (openrouter.ai)
MODEL_TYPE=openrouter
MODEL_KEY=sk-or-v1-...

# Optional: Override default endpoints
# SEPOLIA_RPC=https://ethereum-sepolia-rpc.publicnode.com
# PIMLICO_API_KEY=pim_...
# AGC_TOKEN_ADDRESS=0x...
# AGENT_PAYMASTER_ADDRESS=0x...
